+# v96.6.0
+
+- Added full property-carrying split sleeper clock support for qualifying 7+ hour SB and 2+ hour OFF/SB periods totaling at least 10 hours.
+- Added pending/provisional split guidance, completed-pair calculations, standard-clock comparison, and split-aware graph violation ranges.
